WEBVTT

00:00:58.415 --> 00:01:01.838
And we call B "the Scrapper,"

00:01:01.862 --> 00:01:04.934
the one who had to fight
against tremendous odds

00:01:04.958 --> 00:01:07.224
to get to the same point.

00:01:08.260 --> 00:01:11.740
You just heard a human resources
director refer to people

00:01:11.764 --> 00:01:13.488
as Silver Spoons and Scrappers --

00:01:13.512 --> 00:01:14.513
(Laughter)

00:01:14.537 --> 00:01:18.916
which is not exactly politically correct
and sounds a bit judgmental.

00:01:18.940 --> 00:01:23.340
But before my human resources
certification gets revoked --

00:01:23.364 --> 00:01:24.484
(Laughter)

00:01:24.508 --> 00:01:25.889
let me explain.

00:01:26.730 --> 00:01:29.063
A resume tells a story.

00:01:29.087 --> 00:01:32.417
And over the years, I've learned
something about people